OL,7,FAvon and Somerset Police arrested more
OL,8,Fthan 200 motorists in their annual
OL,9,Fcrackdown on drink or drug driving
OL,10,Fover the festive season.
OL,12,FThe force says drink and drug driving
OL,13,Fwas a factor in a quarter of all fatal
OL,14,Fcrashes in its policing area in 2025.
OL,16,FA total of 243 drivers were arrested
OL,17,Fon suspicion of drink or drug driving
OL,18,Fbetween 1 and 28 December 2025.
