OL,7,FLast night, New Year's Eve, officers
OL,8,Fwarned motorists once again to "expect
OL,9,Fto be pulled over" as police target
OL,10,Fthose who get behind the wheel while
OL,11,Funder the influence of drink or drugs.
OL,13,FRevellers were urged to plan their
OL,14,Fjourneys ahead by booking public
OL,15,Ftransport, nominating a designated
OL,16,Fdriver or arranging alternative
OL,17,Faccommodation, instead of taking the
OL,18,Frisk and getting behind the wheel
OL,19,Fwhile intoxicated.
