OL,4,Cpeople on suspicion of drink or drug
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FMore than 200 vehicles were stopped as
OL,8,Fpart of the Christmas campaign against
OL,9,Fdrink and drug driving in the Weston-
OL,10,Fsuper-Mare area alone on December 27.
OL,12,FOf those drivers, two failed to stop
OL,13,Fand will be pursued for prosecution,
OL,14,Fone driver was reported for document
OL,15,Foffences and summoned to court, one
OL,16,Funinsured vehicle was seized, and
OL,17,Fanother vehicle was seized because the
OL,18,Fdriver did not have a licence. Nine
OL,19,Fother traffic offences ` ranging from
OL,20,Fnot wearing a seatbelt to bald tyres `
OL,21,Fwere also reported.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
