OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,FOne driver was also arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of drug driving and has been
OL,9,Freleased under investigation.
OL,11,FPC Nick Steele, a member of the roads
OL,12,Fpolicing team, said: "At this time of
OL,13,Fthe year we inherently do see an
OL,14,Fincrease in these types of offences,
OL,15,Fand it's down to the festivities,
OL,16,Fparties, finishing work early, and
OL,17,Fpeople run the risk of having one,
OL,18,Ftwo, or three drinks and think they
OL,19,Fare safe to drive home. Drivers should
OL,20,Fexpect to get pulled over.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
