OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,F"People have worked hard all year,
OL,8,Fand, for some, this can be the only
OL,9,Fopportunity to let off steam. But,
OL,10,Fbefore they do, we want them to plan
OL,11,Fhow they are getting home, don't drive
OL,12,For ride a motorbike that day, lift
OL,13,Fshare, jump in with the designated
OL,14,Fdriver who is on soft drinks, use
OL,15,Fpublic transport.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
