OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police arrest 243
OL,4,Cpeople on suspicion of drink or drug
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,F"We want people to have a great time
OL,8,Fbut if they are drinking, we don't
OL,9,Fwant them behind the wheel. There have
OL,10,Fbeen cases I have dealt with which
OL,11,Fhave proven to me some shocking
OL,12,Fbehaviour.
OL,14,F"I have had drivers who have provided
OL,15,Fincredibly high readings at the
OL,16,Froadside, and they have had children
OL,17,Fin the car, or they have been in
OL,18,Fcollisions where people have been hurt
OL,19,For have sadly lost their lives.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
