OL,3,CAvon and Somerset Police arrest 243
OL,4,Cpeople on suspicion of drink or drug
OL,5,Cdriving
OL,7,F"Some people show remorse but, more
OL,8,Foften than not, they don't."
OL,10,FA total of 427 fatal and serious
OL,11,Fcollisions were reported in 2025, with
OL,12,Fdrink or drugs being listed as a
OL,13,Ffactor in 12% of those.
OL,15,FInspector Matt Boiles said: "There is
OL,16,Fno safe way to drink and drive ` not
OL,17,Fat Christmas, not on New Year's Eve,
OL,18,Fnot any day of the year.
OL,26,@wD@]OU
