OL,7,F"Even small amounts of alcohol or
OL,8,Fdrugs can seriously impair your
OL,9,Fjudgement, reaction times, and
OL,10,Fcoordination, putting lives at risk.
OL,12,F"Don't be tempted to take chances, we
OL,13,Fwill be out there conducting checks
OL,14,Fand responding to intelligence."
